d comfortable back support whether you're leaning forward, sitting upright, or reclining, effectively relieving lower back pain from long-term use.<\/li><li>4D Ergonomic Neck Pillow: Unlike regular headrests, AutoFull G7 desk chair offers forward and backward adjustment with a larger dual-axis rotation range, adapting to various gaming, working, or studying postures, providing comfortable neck support and relieving neck pain from prolonged use, catering to different body types and movements.<\/li><li>720° Dual-Axis Rotating Armrests: The armrests on this computer chair offer full 720° rotation and multi-dimensional adjustments, including 2.76-inch height adjustment, 2.36-inch front-back sliding, and 360° rotation for both the armrest surface and handle, ensuring stable arm support for different scenarios, preventing arm pain during long sessions.<\/li><li>140° Zero-Gravity Recline: With 4-position free-stop adjustment, our desk chair meets the reclining needs for office work, watching videos, and taking breaks. The Auto-balance induction chassis allows smooth reclining for light users and easy standing up for heavy users, perfect for relaxing activities.<\/li><li>Precise Fit for Various Body Types: All components of the AutoFull office chair are height-adjustable, precisely fitting users from 5.1ft to 6.5ft. Adjustments include 1.57-inch lumbar support, 2.56-inch backrest, 1.77-inch headrest, 3.15-inch seat height, 2.76-inch armrest, and 1.97-inch sliding seat cushion, ensuring everyone finds their ideal sitting position.<\/li><li>Stylish DesStylish Design & RGB Lighting: The unique RGB lighting module on the office chair creates a cool gaming atmosphere. The removable laser-back panel allows for quick customization without screws, letting you design your chair's appearance and create a personalized space.ign & RGB Lighting: The unique RGB lighting module on the office chair creates a cool gaming atmosphere. The removable laser-back panel allows for quick customization without screws, letting you design your chair's appearance and create a personalized space.<\/li><li>Durability & Safety: In line with BIFMA international standards, the AutoFull gaming chair meets top - level quality and safety requirements. It uses a Level 4 cylinder with SGS\/TUV dual accreditation for maximum safety. Plus, its PU - wrapped quiet wheels protect floors and move silently.<\/li><li>After-sales Service: AutoFull gaming chair provides users with 36 months of parts replacement or repair service. If you have any suggestions for our computer chair, please feel free to contact us.<\/li><\/ul>","page":""}},"collapsible_text_qEYXRB":{"type":"collapsible_text","disabled":true,"settings":{"enable_group":true,"font_transform":"capitalize","background_group":"","icon":"none","icon_width":20,"title":"WHAT'S INCLUDED","content":"<p>Share some content to your customers about your products.<\/p>","page":""}},"collapsible_text_Dn9Bhc":{"type":"collapsible_text","disabled":true,"settings":{"enable_group":true,"font_transform":"capitalize","background_group":"","icon":"none","icon_width":20,"title":"Shipping Policy","content":"<p>Free Shipping – No minimum purchase required (available regions only).<\/p><p>Available Region: United States<\/p><p>Restricted shipping destinations include Puerto Rico (PR), Hawaii (HI), Guam (GU), and Alaska (AK).<\/p><p>Processing: 1-2 business days<\/p><p>Delivery: 3-7 business days via FedEx\/UPS<\/p><p>Tracking: Email sent with tracking number upon shipment<\/p><p>* Exceptions may apply to distant and\/or less accessible locations. We do not ship to PO boxes and Military APO, FPO and DPO destinations. <\/p>","page":""}},"collapsible_text_wzAPgV":{"type":"collapsible_text","disabled":true,"settings":{"enable_group":true,"font_transform":"capitalize","background_group":"","icon":"none","icon_width":20,"title":"Return Policy","content":"<p>Returns Accepted Within 14 Days<\/p><p>✔ Unused, original condition & packaging<\/p><p>✔ Proof o